title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Florio/Grimm/Zimmer/Neal III
description: -- Nordo fills in for PA for the next couple days, Mike Florio opens the show to talk Vikings and their playoff hopes, Mike Grimm talks Gophers Hoops as well as Axe Week against Wisconsin, we hear the Mike Zimmer Presser, Producer Brett gives the Sports Essentials, and in the final hour Lavelle E Neal III joins to talk Vikings Bears, as well as some MLB news.
